						<summary>

						<p>This is also a label inscription of three lines of writing. The figure is that of a man holding a club in each of his hands. The inscription refers to a threatened destruction of the village and its rescue by one Vaḷaiñjiyaṉ Iḷaiyāṉ Kāḍaṉ who fell in the attempt.</p>						

